        <h2>Use case diagrams</h2>
        <p>
            These are the use case narratives for Subsystem 2: User Subsytem. I have chosen to make the narratives for only one subsystem,
            as it would become rather lengthy to mark if I had narratives for all subsystems.
        </p>
        <p>
            The user subsystem has 7 main use cases, which pertain to users in general. That means that the use cases apply to all users who are subclasses of class user, as well.
            This includes Students, Educators and Administrators. I chose to group these use cases together to avoid having to redundantly repeat the exact same use cases for 
            different subsystems/users.
        </p>
        <br />
        @Html.ActionLink("Download narratives", "DownloadUC", "File", null, new { @class = "btn btn-success" })
